# ğŸš— BT-RoboCar â€“ Bluetooth-Controlled Smart Car  

BT-RoboCar is a **Bluetooth-controlled robotic car** powered by **ESP32 and Arduino**. It allows remote control via a mobile app, enabling movement and robotic arm operations. The ESP32 acts as a **bridge**, receiving commands from the mobile app via **Bluetooth** and forwarding them to the Arduino through **Serial1** to execute actions.  

## âœ¨ Features  
- ğŸ“¡ **Bluetooth Control** â€“ Wirelessly control the car using a mobile app.  
- ğŸ® **Real-Time Commands** â€“ Sends movement and robotic arm actions instantly.  
- ğŸ”„ **ESP32-Arduino Communication** â€“ Serial communication between ESP32 and Arduino.  
- âš™ï¸ **Expandable & Customizable** â€“ Easily add new features like sensors or automation.  

